@startuml TourCreationAndDiscoveryFlow
title Tour Creation / Tour Discovery

skinparam swimlaneWidth same
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam activityBorderColor #2F6FED
skinparam conditionStyle diamond
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8E1
skinparam noteBorderColor #D97706

|#LightBlue|Admin|
|#Lavender|System|
|#LightBlue|Customer|

|Admin|
:Step 1: Inputs tour details;

|System|
:Step 2: Validates tour data;

if (Valid?) then (No)
  :Step 3 (If Invalid):\nDisplays validation error;

  |Admin|
  :Step 4: Edits tour information;

  |System|
  :Re-validates (back to Step 2);
else (Yes)
  :Step 5 (If Valid):\nSaves and publishes tour;
endif

|Customer|
:Step 6: Accesses home page;

:Step 7: Searches and filters tours;

|System|
:Step 8: Queries active tours;

if (Match?) then (No)
  :Step 9 (If No Match):\nDisplays "No Tours Found";

  |Customer|
  :Step 10: Retries search;

  |System|
  :Re-queries (back to Step 8);
else (Yes)
  :Step 11 (If Match):\nDisplays matching tours;

  |Customer|
  :Step 12: Selects and views tour;
endif

note over Admin, Customer
  Sub-flow 1: Tour Creation Flow  (Step 1 - 5)
  Sub-flow 2: Tour Discovery Flow (Step 6 - 12)
end note

@enduml